    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain and rinse the <strong>black beans </strong>and <strong>champagne lentils</strong></p><p>Dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>in 650ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.3L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
