    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pick a few leaves from the <strong>dill</strong>, <strong>coriander</strong>, <strong>mint </strong>and <strong>parsley </strong>and set aside for garnish</p><p>Pick the <strong>remaining mint leaves </strong>from their stalks, then chop all of the <strong>herbs </strong>together roughly, discard the mint stalks</p>",
