      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the leek has softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>to the pot with the <strong>ground turmeric </strong>and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p><p>Add the <strong>vegetable stock </strong>with the <strong>spinach</strong>, <strong>chopped herbs </strong>and <strong>soy sauce </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Season generously with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p>",
