    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>fine egg noodles </strong>to the pot and stir them with a fork until separated and beginning to soften</p><p>Add the <strong>drained black beans </strong>and <strong>lentils </strong>to the pot with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 2-3 min further or until the noodles are tender and everything’s warmed through</p>",
