    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>warming herby Persian-style noodle soup </strong>in bowls</p><p>Top with a dollop of <strong>soured cream </strong>and sprinkle over the <strong>crispy onions</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>reserved herbs </strong>and a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
